</head><body><table border=0 align=center width=80%><tr><td><center><h1>Earring of the Solstice</h1><br>by Xanthe Ravenwolf</center><br><div align="center">
  <center>
  <table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="border-collapse: collapse" bordercolor="#111111" width="573" id="AutoNumber1">
    <tr>
      <td width="573">
  <p align="center">This is a trade-skill heavy quest. Alternatively you can 
  purchase the components for the final combine in bazaar. Original quest and 
  much of the info for this guide are credited to
  <a href="http://www.eqtraders.com/quests/potc_intro.htm">Xanthe and EQTraders</a>. 
  Listed below are the various items you must obtain for the quest. For details 
  on recipes and the related, I encourage you to visit their site.</p>

  <hr noshade>

      <h4><b>Gifts of the Elves</b></h4>
  <p><font color="#6633CC"><b>Demi-Sec Champagne </b>(<i>brewing trivial >250)</i></font></p>
  <ul>
    <li>Demi Sec Champage = 1 Champagne Magnum + 1 Soda Water +
    <a href="http://www.eqtraders.com/location/brewing.htm">1 Wine Yeast + 2 
    Grapes</a> </li>
  </ul>
  <p><font color="#6633CC"><b>Mistletoe Cutting Sickle </b>(<i>smithing trivial 
  >250</i>)</font></p>
  <ul>
    <li>Mistletoe Cutting Sickle= Blessed Sickle Blade + Blessed Sickle Hilt + 
    Blessed Sickle Pommel + Smithy Hammer </li>
  </ul>
  <p><font color="#6633CC"> </font><b><font color="#6633CC">Golden Idol of 
  Tunare </font></b><font color="#6633CC">(<i>pottery trivial 242</i>)</font></p>
  <ul>
    <li>Unfired Golden Idol of Tunare= 1 Gold Bar+ 1 Idol Sketch + 1 enchanted 
    block of clay + 1 water + 1 Celestial Essence + Sculpting Tools + 1 Vial of 
    Distilled Mana + 1 Imbued Emerald </li>
    <li>Then combine Unfired Golden Idol of Tunare + Divine Crystalline Glaze + 
    High Quality Firing Sheet </li>
  </ul>
  <p> </p>
  <hr align="left" width="200" noShade>
  <h4><b>Gifts of the Halflings</b></h4>
  <p><b><font color="#6633CC">Lotus Pie </font></b><font color="#6633CC">(<i>baking 
  trivial 236</i>)</font></p>
  <ul>
    <li>Lotus Pie (miraculous meal, CHA 9) = Thick Lotus Paste + Clump of Dough 
    + Pie Tin </li>
  </ul>
  <p> </p>
  <p><b><font color="#6633CC">Misty Thicket Picnic </font></b>
  <font color="#6633CC">(<i>baking trivial >250</i>)</font></p>
  <ul>
    <li>Misty Thicket Picnic (miraculous meal, STR 5, STA 5, WIS 5, INT 5, size: 
    large) = 1 Picnic Basket + 1 Marmalade Sandwich + 1 Jumjum Spiced Beer + 1 
    Jumjum Salad + 1 Royal Mints + 1 Mature Cheese + 2 (unstacked) Jumjum Cake 
    Slices </li>
  </ul>
  <p><b><font color="#6633CC">Lucky Cabbage </font></b><font color="#6633CC">(<i>baking 
  trivial 182</i>)</font></p>
  <ul>
    <li>Lucky Cabbage <i>(meal, CHA 10)</i> = 1 Wild Cabbage + Blessed Dust of 
    Karana </li>
  </ul>
  <p><br>
 </p>
  <hr align="left" width="200" noShade>
  <h4><b>Gifts of Mankind</b></h4>
  <p><font color="#6633CC"><b>Blessed Fishing Rod </b>(<i>fishing trivial >200</i>)
  </font></p>
  <ul>
    <li>Blessed Fishing Rod = Branch of Planar Oak + Celestial Essence + Blessed 
    Dust of Karana + Spool + treated silk fibers </li>
  </ul>
  <p><font color="#6633CC"> <b>Star Ruby Encrusted Stein </b>(<i>pottery trivial 
  >250</i>)</font></p>
  <ul>
    <li>Unfired Star Ruby Encrusted Stein = Lacquered Star Ruby + Large Block of 
    Magic Clay + Sculpting Tools + Ceramic Lining Sketch + water + Celestial 
    Essence (</li>
    <li>Then combine: Unfired Star Ruby Encrusted Stein +<a href="http://www.eqtraders.com/location/pottery.htm"> 
    High Quality Firing Sheet</a> = Star Ruby Encrusted Stein</li>
  </ul>
  <p><font color="#6633CC"><b>Ceremonial Solstice Robe </b>(<i>tailoring trivial 
  >250)</i></font></p>
  <ul>
    <li>Combine: Gem Studded Chain + 3 Sacred Tunare Silks (unstacked) + Tunic 
    Pattern + Embroidery Needle </li>
  </ul>
  <p> </p>
  <hr align="left" width="200" noShade>
  <p>Once you have all 9 gifts, place them in a forge and combine (100% success 
  rate) and you will receive Xanthe's Earring of Nature and a copy of protection 
  of the cabbage (which you can discard, being a silly druid spell). Take 
  Xanthe's earring and give it to Rebecca Cabbageleaf who is inside one of the 
  buildings in Fungus Grove. She will hand you your brand new Earring of the 
  Solstice. </p>
  <p> </p>

      </div>

